## Trigger Phrase Error Protocol (LAW 8 — always active)
If Kelly says any of these → STOP, log error, fix, confirm:
- "Why did you" → something Rex did was wrong
- "That's wrong" → incorrect output
- "WTF" → something badly broken
- "Why are you" → Rex behaving incorrectly
Required: immediate journal entry + PR + visible 🚨 confirmation block

